{"source": "https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/chenpokong/js-05092023110713.html", "type": "NewsArticle", "published time": "2023-05-09T11:08:00-04:00", "modified time": "2023-05-09T17:04:21-04:00", "author": null, "publisher": {"type": "Organization", "name": "Radio Free Asia"}, "title": "\u8bc4\u8bba | \u9648\u7834\u7a7a\uff1a\u4e60\u738b\u5f53\u9053\uff0c\u5c31\u662f\u4e00\u80a1\u9006\u6d41\u3002\u5386\u53f2\u89c1\u5f97\u591a\u4e86", "description": "\u4eca\u5e74\u4e94\u56db\uff0c\u4e2d\u5171\u8ba2\u7acb\u7684\u4e2d\u56fd\u9752\u5e74\u8282\uff0c\u515a\u5a92\u53d1\u8868\u4e60\u8fd1\u5e73\u7684\u4e24\u5c01\u56de\u4fe1\uff0c\u4e00\u5c01\u56de\u7ed9\u519c\u4e1a\u5927\u5b66\u7684\u4e0b\u4e61\u5b66\u751f\uff0c\u9f13\u52b1\u4ed6\u4eec\u201c\u6df1\u5165\u7530\u95f4\u5730\u5934\u548c\u6751\u5c6f\u519c\u5bb6\u3002\u201d", "videos": [], "audios": ["https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/chenpokong/js-05092023110713.html/@@stream"], "text": "<img src=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/chenpokong/js-05092023110713.html/@@images/f32b8014-be1d-4579-81aa-71f611ffb57a.jpeg\"/>\n\u4e2d\u5171\u603b\u4e66\u8bb0\u4e60\u8fd1\u5e73\u5728\u4e8c\u5341\u5927\u4e0a\u83b7\u5f97\u8fde\u4efb\n<a href=\"https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/pinglun/chenpokong/js-05092023110713.html/@@images/image\">\n</a>\n\u7f8e\u8054\u793e\u56fe\u7247\n<!-- zoomattribute -->\n<script language=\"javascript\" type=\"text/javascript\">\n var audio_title = {\"audio_name\": \"\\u8bc4\\u8bba | \\u9648\\u7834\\u7a7a\\uff1a\\u4e60\\u738b\\u5f53\\u9053\\uff0c\\u5c31\\u662f\\u4e00\\u80a1\\u9006\\u6d41\\u3002\\u5386\\u53f2\\u89c1\\u5f97\\u591a\\u4e86\"};\n</script>\n<script>\n eventer = function(id){\n            var data = {\n                    \"tealium_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"on_page_event\" : \"audio_play\",\n                    \"audio_name\": audio_title['audio_name'],\n                    \"article_uid\": utag_data[\"article_uid\"],\n                    \"media_type\": \"onDemand audio\",\n  